name: Summoned Katana
description: Summoned Katana is a Rare Harvesting Tool in Fortnite: Battle Royale, that can be purchased in the Item Shop for  800 V-Bucks or with the Mr. Meeseeks Bundle for  2,100 V-Bucks. Summoned Katana was first released in Chapter 3: Season 4 and is part of the Mr. Meeseeks Set.

name: Neutrino Bomb
description: The Neutrino Bomb is a powerful bomb invented by Rick Sanchez that could potentially wipe out all life on Earth and other planets.

name: Laser Gun
description: Rick's laser gun (sometimes referred to as ray gun or laser pistol), is a firearm owned and commonly in the possession of Rick Sanchez. It is a magazine-fed, semi-automatic/channeled, directed-energy weapon presumably of Rick's own design. For the first two seasons it is Rick's main weapon of choice against most humanoid threats.

name: Portal pistol
description: The Portal Pistol is a gadget that allows the user(s) to travel between different universes/dimensions/realities. The device was likely created by the Dinosaurs.

name: Pulse Rifle
description: Pulse Rifles were Galactic Federation-standard military rifles used by Gromflomite soldiers. They were first seen in the episode Pilot, where Rick and Morty were attacked by Gromflomite Guards wielding the rifles.
